          added it


          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780671413705" href="/book/show/274855.The_Claw_of_the_Conciliator">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10445368-kevin-kelsey?shelf=read-2016">read-2016</a>
